## 3. Technical Stack (Recommended)

| Layer | Technology | Rationale |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Frontend** | React / Next.js | Best-in-class SEO and speed via Server-Side Rendering (SSR). |
| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS | Rapid UI development with responsive utility classes. |
| **Backend** | Node.js (App Dir) | Unified React/Server logic in Next.js. |
| **Database** | MongoDB Atlas | Scalable document storage (NoSQL) for flexible event data. |
| **Auth** | NextAuth.js | Secure OAuth & credential-based authentication. |

